            "type": "text",
            "text": "Built a dynamic portfolio website powered by a Strapi headless CMS, enabling real-time content updates without code changes. Implemented admin authentication and role-based access to manage profile, skills, education, and project entries. Developed a frontend in React and TailwindCSS, consuming REST APIs to fetch and display content. Ensured mobile responsiveness and optimized SEO with meta tags and dynamic routing using React Router. Deployed backend on Render and frontend on Vercel for fast and scalable delivery."
